.faq
  .hero-unit.parallax
    .slogan
      .container-fluid
        .row
          .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2.text-center
            p.faq-title
              | FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS
        
  .container-fluid
    .row
      .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
        .panel.panel-default.no-border#faq-accordian
        
          / First Panel
          .panel-heading.faq-panel-header#heading-1
            h3.panel-title.faq-panel-title
              a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#faq-accordian" href="#faq-collapse-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-collapse-1"
                | 1. HOW DO I BOOK AN APPOINTMENT?
          #faq-collapse-1.panel-collapse.collapse.text-center aria-labelledby="heading-1"
            .panel-body.text-left.faq-panel-padding
              p.read-more-text Search the types of beauty services according to your budget. MOD will detect the available slots nearest to you, right now at your fingertips for FREE!
              p.read-more-text
                | You may read more on 
                = link_to "How it works.", how_it_works_path, class: "how-it-works-link"    
          
          / Second Panel
          .panel-heading.faq-panel-header#heading-2
            h3.panel-title.faq-panel-title
              a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#faq-accordian" href="#faq-collapse-2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-collapse-2"
                | 2. WHERE CAN I BOOK AN APPOINTMENT?
    
          #faq-collapse-2.panel-collapse.collapse.text-center aria-labelledby="heading-2"
            .panel-body.text-left.faq-panel-padding
              p.read-more-text MOD will be available in Bangsar as the firt city center launch and will expand to other locations as we grow.
    
