                | 3. HOW DO I VIEW OR CANCEL AN APPOINTMENT?
   
          #faq-collapse-3.panel-collapse.collapse.text-center aria-labelledby="heading-3"
            .panel-body.text-left.faq-panel-padding
              p.read-more-text You will receive a confirmation code and cancellation SMS link for every booking you make.
              
          / Fourth Panel
          .panel-heading.faq-panel-header#heading-4
            h3.panel-title.faq-panel-title
              a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#faq-accordian" href="#faq-collapse-4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-collapse-4"
                | 4. HOW DO I CHANGE THE TIME OF MY APPOINTMENT?
    
          #faq-collapse-4.panel-collapse.collapse.text-center aria-labelledby="heading-4"
            .panel-body.text-left.faq-panel-padding
              p.read-more-text You can choose to contact the salon directly in your confirmation SMS link.
              
